                    <span>I used to waste time obsessing over why my boyfriend dumped me and why I had not achieved what I wanted financially until I read this book.  Eckhart Tolle explains WHY you should let go of the past and move into the present moment. He exlains that if you refuse to forgive others, you are resisting life. He motivates you to live in the now with the WHY! Another wonderful book, Optimal Thinking: How To Be Your Best Self, teaches you HOW to deal most effectively with disturbing feelings, overcome sef-sabotage and how to make the most of the present moment.  I absolutely recommend each of these books.</span>
                  
