                    <span>When first introduced to this book, I was highly skeptical.  After all, I have already read many religious, spiritual and philosophical texts.  Reading was able to fulfill me momentarily, and there was a gradual "let-down" as spiritual sensations became "medusa"d into cold stone intellectual mind-stuff.  This book was able to point past itself, allowed me to watch myself inspite of mind-stuff, and to be able to find peace in the present moment.  A must have for all seekers.</span>
                  
              
